rigin":26084,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Khadijah: Good news of Paradise for the Prophet&#8217;s wife","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Angel Gabriel came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, here is Khadijah coming to you with a dish of stew, food, and drink. When she arrives before you, greet her with peace on behalf of her\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27515,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/11\/ramadan-jibreel-quran-twice\/","url_meta":{"origin":26084,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Gabriel comes to review the Quran twice","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Fatimah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cGabriel would come to me to revise the Quran once every year. This year he revised with me twice. I do not think it means anything but that my term will come to an end. Verily, you will be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8194,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/friendship-prophet-khadijah\/","url_meta":{"origin":26084,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Friends: The Prophet keeps relations with Khadijah&#8217;s friends","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was given something, he would say, \u201cGo to such person, for they were a friend of Khadijah. Go to the house of such person, for they were loved by Khadijah.\" Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad 225 Grade:\u00a0Hasan\u00a0(fair) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":22075,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/02\/25\/nikah-your-wife-treat-well\/","url_meta":{"origin":26084,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Marriage: She is your wife, if you treat her well","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 25, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Hujr ibn Qays reported: Ali, may Allah be pleased with him, offered a marriage proposal to Fatimah, daughter of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him. The Prophet said, \u201cShe is yours, if you treat her with the best company.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r 3490 Grade: Sahih (authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7736,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/aisha-khadija-jealous-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":26084,"position":5},"title":"Aisha on Khadijah: I was never jealous of any woman like Khadijah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"'Urwah reported: Aisha, may Allah be pleased with her, said, \"I never felt so jealous about any woman as I did for Khadijah. She had died three year